1938 FIFA WORLD CUP 1954 FIFA WORLD CUP Section::::1954 FIFA World Cup .
According to journalist Henry Guldemont , some of his Swiss colleagues regarded the 1954 Belgian team as " favourites for the world title " after a promising 4–4 opener against England .
However , in the second and last group match against Italy , Belgium was defeated 1–4 and was unable to proceed to the finals . !
