In the first game of the 1982 FIFA World Cup , held at Camp Nou , Belgium celebrated one of their most famous victories :
a 0–1 win over defending champions Argentina with a goal by Erwin Vandenbergh .
After pushing through to the second group stage of that tournament , Belgium was stunned by a Polish hat - trick from Zbigniew Boniek .
The decisive match against the Soviet Union ended in a 0–1 loss . !
